{"tid":2162102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平高喊公有制主體決不動搖  李克強：救小企業","createTime":"2020-08-18T02:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T05:00:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1db968907c24022bde6c7bb4cc747e42fefa979c","tid":2162102,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"中國總理李克強周一（17日）在北京露面，外界預料北戴河會議已結束。李克強在主持國務院會議期間，強調要確保對小微企業的政策資助。另一方面，中共黨刊《求是》雜誌周日（16日）刊發中共總書記習近平5年前一番講話，強調「公有制主體地位不能動搖」，有分析指出，《求是》刊載這篇講話，顯示習近平意欲「反撲」...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www-rfa-org.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/state-08172020062613.html/china-state.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-rfa-org.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fstate-08172020062613.html%2Fchina-state.png&h=f68b3bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/state-08172020062613.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Fstate-08172020062613.html&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkFxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=db08011a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/state-08172020062613.html</a>"},{"pid":"6f20e2f38e619e24fad1c1d1041d0db9ce32d2c0","tid":2162102,"uid":152589,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T02:59:17.000Z","msg":"衰啲講句 李克強一定要失勢 先可以繼續加速"},{"pid":"d4dbb6daee01963c76c549c09c3024a588490f49","tid":2162102,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T02:59:27.000Z","msg":"反撲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c8a00148c2975c3644dfe80d297535674d7241","tid":2162102,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1db968907c24022bde6c7bb4cc747e42fefa979c","tid":2162102,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T02:54:21.000Z","msg":"中國總理李克強周一（17日）在北京露面，外界預料北戴河會議已結束。李克強在主持國務院會議期間，強調要確保對小微企業